---
title: Sri Lankan Style Coconutty Hake Curry with Courgettes, Green Beans and Rice
description: We love good Sri Lankan Hake Curry, Courgette & Rice and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
